title: 12 Rare 80s Albums [Part 68] Post-Punk, New Wave, Synthwave
description:
A little treasure from Captain 80s to all the Pirates to take with them before the ship goes down! This time around I am posting 12 records instead of the normal 4 you would get. Hope you enjoy and seed them until Pirates are no longer around.... ok, let's see what we have in this little treasure box, hummmmmmm....

 

Bunnydrums - Holy Moly [1984]

Dance Macabre - Dance Macabre [1983]

DeFilm - DeFilm [1985]

Elements - Elementary (1981)

European Toys - Nine Men Applauding [1985]

Gleaming Spires - Welcoming A New Ice Age [1985]

Idle Eyes - Idle Eyes [1985]

Jon St. James - Trans-Atlantic [1984]

Los Microwaves - Life After Breakfast [1982]

Tattoo Host - Vision On [1980]

The Elektrics - State of Shock [1981]

Trek With Quintronic - Trek W Quintronic [1981]
